sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant GW as Gateway / Ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Route as HTTPRoute /<br/>VirtualService
    participant SVC as {isvc}-predictor Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Pod as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant SDK as KServe SDK<br/>(v1/v2/OpenAI)
    participant S3 as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,SDK: Flow 1: InferenceService Model Serving (Raw Deployment)

    Client->>GW: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>Auth: OAuth / Kuadrant
    GW->>Route: Forward (in-cluster)<br/>Header injection
    Route->>SVC: Route to Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    SVC->>Pod: Forward to Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    Pod->>SDK: Inference Request
    SDK-->>Pod: Prediction Result
    Pod-->>SVC: Response
    SVC-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>GW: Response
    GW-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService with Scheduler (P/D Disaggregated)

    participant GW2 as Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant IPool as InferencePool /<br/>HTTPRoute
    participant EPP as Scheduler (EPP)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant Decode as Decode Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS (self-signed)
    participant Prefill as Prefill Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS (self-signed)

    Client->>GW2: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: AuthPolicy
    GW2->>IPool: Route via HTTPRoute<br/>to InferencePool
    IPool->>EPP: gRPC PickEndpoint<br/>9002/TCP TLS (self-signed)
    EPP->>Decode: Forward to Decode<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS (self-signed)
    Decode->>Prefill: Prefill request (P/D)<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS (self-signed)
    Prefill-->>Decode: Prefill KV-cache
    Decode-->>EPP: Inference Result
    EPP-->>IPool: Response
    IPool-->>GW2: Response
    GW2-->>Client: Streaming JSON Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Model Download (Storage Initializer)

    participant PodInit as Pod Init Phase
    participant SI as storage-initializer<br/>(Python Init Container)
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>/mnt/models

    PodInit->>SI: Start init container
    SI->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / GCP ADC / Azure SP / HF Token
    S3-->>SI: Model artifacts
    SI->>FS: Write to /mnt/models
    SI-->>PodInit: Init complete

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: WVA Autoscaling

    participant LCtrl as llmisvc-controller
    participant VWA as WVA Controller<br/>(llmd.ai)
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant HPA as HPA / KEDA

    LCtrl->>VWA: Create VariantAutoscaling CR<br/>K8s API HTTPS
    VWA->>Prom: Query metrics<br/>HTTPS Bearer Token
    Prom-->>VWA: wva_desired_replicas
    VWA->>VWA: Publish external metric
    HPA->>Prom: Read external metric<br/>HTTPS Bearer Token
    HPA->>LCtrl: Scale Deployment / LWS replicas<br/>K8s API HTTPS
